title: How do we configure voting power?
body:
When we vote we see voting power 0 SQUID even though we have more than 0 SQUIDs in our wallets. We do not know why we do not see the voting power equivalent to our SQUIDs. 

We ask the community to help us by voting on the options in this proposal or reach to us in [discord](https://discord.gg/Su7h33xd)
choices: Send me SQUIDs to help testing.
author: 0xa7910BEF6dfdFC0d35962bEE7f8716BBBcDA1330
